  "title": "[사당추나요법/허리디스크/체형교정이수한의원]퇴행성 허리디스크",
  "addDate": "2013. 4. 3.",
  "categoryNo": "13",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110165273267",
  "html_size": 191989,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110165273267\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110165273267\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t \r\n<div style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\" class=\"view\">\r\n<div style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'; FONT-SIZE: 10pt\" class=\"view\">\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">[사당추나요법/허리디스크/체형교정이수한의원]</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">퇴행성 허리디스크</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">비가 오는 날이면 더 아픈거 같은 허리 통증</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">오늘은 퇴행성 허리디스크에 대해서 알아보도록 하겠습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8f3441329750bcc5.png\" width=\"327\" height=\"355\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 327px; rheight: 355px\" id=\"20130403_195/isuhani_1364919857043lDfU9_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE1.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/8f3441329750bcc5.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">퇴행성 디스크란 디스크와 뼈가 나이가 들면서 생기는 병입니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">디스크의 수핵은&nbsp; 나이가 들면 수분이 빠져 나가게 되어 충격을 잘 흡수 하지 못하고 작은 충격에도</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">손상을 받게 됩니다 이는 수년간에 걸처서 발생 하게 되고, MRI를 촬영하게 되면</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;정상적인 디스크는 하얗게 나타나는데 반해 퇴행성 디스크는 까맣게 나타나게 됩니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">또한 주로 특정 한두 부위에 문제가 발생하는 것과는 달리 여러 부위에 동시 다발적으로 퇴행이 진행될 확률이 높습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">디스크의 퇴행이 발생되면 척추에 가해지는 충격을 효과적으로 흡수하지 못하여 뼈가 가시처럼 자라는 골극이 생겨</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">신경을 자극하여 염증을 발생시켜 통증을 일으키기도하고 또한 척추뼈 양쪽 뛰에 위아래를 연결 시켜주는 척추 후관절이 존재 하는데</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">퇴행성 관절여밍 생기게 되면 허리 통증이 발생하게 됩니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이러한 퇴행성 디스크는 주로 50대 이상에서 나타나는 것이 일반적이나 최근에는 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">과도한 컴퓨터나 운동부족으로 20~30대에서도 나타나는&nbsp; 사례가 늘어나고 있습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d678bb8d74f71d8a.png\" width=\"259\" height=\"253\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 259px; rheight: 253px\" id=\"20130403_162/isuhani_1364920241138FwKtW_PNG/%C7%E3%B8%AE2.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d678bb8d74f71d8a.png\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 퇴행성 디스크의 증상</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -다리보다는 허리의통증이 주로 나타난다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -만성적으로 허리에 무지근한 통증이 나타난다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -오래 앉아 있거나 서 있으면 허리에 끊어질 듯한 통증이 나타난다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-걸으면 통증이 줄어든다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-아침에 일어나면 허리가 아프고 낮에 활동하면 통증이 줄어드는 경향이 있다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 퇴행성 디스크 원인</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -반복적으로 허리에 부담을 주는동작</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-운동부족으로 인한 근력약화</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -잘못된 자세와 습관</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -흡연 및 스트레스</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -영양 불균형</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;-선천성,유전적 요인</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">디스크 퇴행정도와 통증과의 관계</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">디스크의 퇴행이 심할수록 통증은 심한 것일까요?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">반드시 그런것은 아닙니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">연세가 많으신 분들의 경우 나이가 들수록 디스크의 퇴행 정도가심해지나 통증 줄어드는 경향이 있습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이는 일정 이상 디스크의 퇴행이 진행되게 되면 염증을 일으키는 물질이 더 이상 발생하지않고</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">몸이 그 상태에 적응하기 때문입니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">턱관절 교정</span><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">의 필요한 퍼티 제작중</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/46b8f62d986649d8.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 250px; rheight: 188px\" id=\"20130403_144/isuhani_1364920882585pCfC3_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C6%DB%C6%BC20130314_143837.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/46b8f62d986649d8.jpg\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f350cc12e0512cf.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"188\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 250px; rheight: 188px\" id=\"20130403_130/isuhani_1364920914809pFwaY_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2_%C6%DB%C6%BC20130314_143847.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f350cc12e0512cf.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">굽은허리로 통증을 호소하며 추나및 턱관절 교정을 함으로써&nbsp;통증이 미세하게 나타난 사례</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">퍼티는 맞춤제작으로써 치료 받으러오기전 까지 착용</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f41fa1a7b9b17e48.jpg\" width=\"493\" height=\"413\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 493px; rheight: 413px\" id=\"20130405_74/isuhani_1365124147372XUuzC_JPEG/%C1%A6%B8%F1_%BE%F8%C0%BD.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f41fa1a7b9b17e48.jpg\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><div>\n<iframe src=\"https://mashup.map.naver.com/view.nhn?mid=bl013068484%40s13104608&type=total\" width=\"402\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" onerror=\"return true;\" onabort=\"return true;\" style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:8px;background-color:white;\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 지도\"></iframe>\n</div></div>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #00b0a2\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 이수한의원 진료시간 안내</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f46a07011398cd7a.png\" width=\"547\" height=\"172\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 547px; rheight: 172px\" id=\"20130403_222/isuhani_1364921315270VQBPj_PNG/%C7%D1%C0%C7%BF%F8%C1%F8%B7%E1%BD%C3%B0%A3%C7%A52.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/f46a07011398cd7a.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c7073f2d0c0ce21.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"66\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 266px; rheight: 66px\" id=\"20130403_221/isuhani_1364921317750CJMVN_PNG/2013-03-18_14%3B49%3B33.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A65CAAB3')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3c7073f2d0c0ce21.png\"></p></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
